u of his..."],[4358,4483,"Okay, that is a no."],[5397,5459,"Marco?"]],"69":[[104,166,"Marco?"],[221,304,"Francesca?"],[379,471,"Where's Matteo?"],[642,804,"You lied about him being upstairs?"],[846,950,"That's right, bitch."],[1184,1309,"You guys are both liars."],[1384,1476,"Sometimes."],[1493,1589,"Not always."],[1659,1943,"Whatever benefits the Franconi legacy."],[1956,2047,"What legacy?"],[2081,2243,"Your legacy is garbage."],[2243,2406,"Franconis have standards."],[2452,2581,"And you don't make the cut."],[2623,2673,"I wanted him to"],[2706,2857,"marry my own daughter,"],[2902,3073,"but Matteo..."],[3144,3340,"You infected him."],[3420,3628,"But he'll thank us soon enough"],[3645,3770,"after he's done"],[3770,3995,"with this obsession of you."],[3995,4099,"Matteo definitely"],[4141,4254,"would have married me"],[4254,4416,"if you hadn't shown up."],[4479,4658,"But you're a lucky little bitch."],[4671,4796,"You've managed to survive,"],[4796,4946,"what, three times?"],[5034,5142,"Three times?"],[5142,5276,"Then she's behind the snake"],[5276,5401,"and the drowning, too."],[5522,5689,"You had three chances"],[5689,5797,"to take the hint."],[5822,6014,"But you're just too ignorant."],[6014,6218,"Or maybe you're just too obstinate."],[6277,6464,"But you'll be a good lesson"],[6493,6677,"for those who go against our family."],[6765,6831,"Matteo wants to"],[6831,6936,"make the business legitimate."],[6936,7011,"You don't have to do this"],[7011,7157,"mafia charade anymore."],[7161,7236,"Matteo wants to go a"],[7236,7361,"hundred percent legit."],[7386,7549,"I don't want to do that completely."],[7570,7661,"I like having"],[7661,7866,"the power of life and death."]],"70":[[137,325,"If you really want to send a message,"],[325,508,"you'll kill her nice and slow."],[734,792,"Do you guys want to"],[792,925,"have some fun with her, actually?"],[963,1084,"I know you're on overtime."],[2018,2214,"You turned out to be a looker."],[2248,2381,"God, I wouldn't mind giving up"],[2381,2523,"five minutes, maybe ten."],[2540,2648,"Get away from me!"],[2648,2748,"Oh, hey."],[2773,3019,"No need to be hostile, okay?"],[3194,3390,"Stop playing hard to get, girl."],[3536,3599,"Whoa!"],[3628,3820,"Oh, she's a feisty treat."],[3916,3970,"Hey!"],[4283,4504,"Touch her again, Antonio,"],[4562,4713,"and I'll fucking kill you."]],"71":[[458,608,"Useless cowards."],[671,834,"You must have a death wish, Marco."],[871,959,"And you must have"],[959,1159,"a hell of a drug tolerance."],[1184,1334,"But I'm glad you're here, Matteo."],[1376,1480,"I've got quite the show"],[1480,1593,"in store for you."],[1618,1680,"Get her!"],[2122,2173,"What?"],[2227,2373,"He is the new CEO."],[2389,2656,"These disloyal dogs"],[2677,2902,"forget who their real master is."],[2940,3023,"Traitors!"],[3040,3132,"All of you!"],[3194,3357,"The real traitors are you two,"],[3395,3636,"for betraying me and the one that I love."],[3661,3787,"Yeah, I have no remorse"],[3787,3899,"for what's going to happen next."],[4091,4237,"Foolish boy."],[4312,4525,"I raised you in my home."],[4562,4850,"I offered you food, my own daughter."],[4979,5125,"And this is how you repay me?"],[5309,5559,"I'm the one with no remorse for you."],[5663,5751,"Do it, Dad."],[5780,5889,"He had his chance."],[5889,6022,"Just shoot them both!"]],"72":[[316,400,"Freeze!"],[921,1013,"FBI!"],[1101,1205,"You're under arrest."],[1559,1643,"Arrest?"],[1764,1847,"For what?"],[1868,2068,"Extortion. Money laundering."],[2068,2173,"Racketeering."],[2198,2302,"It's a long list."],[2544,2635,"Matteo."],[2673,2794,"I told you I was cleaning out"],[2794,2894,"the trash in the city."],[2961,3036,"You just didn't get on board"],[3036,3098,"with the program."],[3219,3319,"Get them fuck out of here."],[4375,4546,"Never let me go, okay?"],[4583,4650,"I won't."],[4675,4854,"No one will ever hurt you again, alright?"]],"73":[[204,291,"Oh my God."],[383,525,"I think I felt a kick."],[704,871,"Hi, baby."],[871,1038,"This is your godmother.